### BIẾN MÔI TRƯỜNG
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### ĐẶT HÀNG - ORDER PLACEMENT
### ============================================

### 1. Đặt hàng thanh toán tiền mặt (COD)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/cash-order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "674a1234567890abcdef1234",
      "name": "Áo thun nam",
      "image": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
      "size": "M",
      "color": "Đen",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 250000
    },
    {
      "product_id": "674a1234567890abcdef5678",
      "name": "Quần jean",
      "image": "https://example.com/jean.jpg",
      "size": "L",
      "color": "Xanh",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 450000
    }
  ],
  "address": {
    "full_name": "Nguyễn Văn A",
    "phone_number": "0912345678",
    "province": "Hồ Chí Minh",
    "district": "Quận 1",
    "ward": "Phường Bến Nghé",
    "street": "123 Nguyễn Huệ"
  },
  "shipping_fee": 30000,
  "total_amount": 980000
}

###

### 2. Đặt hàng thanh toán VNPay

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/vnpay-order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "674a1234567890abcdef1234",
      "name": "Áo thun nam",
      "image": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
      "size": "M",
      "color": "Đen",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 250000
    }
  ],
  "address": {
    "full_name": "Nguyễn Văn A",
    "phone_number": "0912345678",
    "province": "Hồ Chí Minh",
    "district": "Quận 1",
    "ward": "Phường Bến Nghé",
    "street": "123 Nguyễn Huệ"
  },
  "shipping_fee": 30000,
  "total_amount": 530000
}

###

### 3. Tạo link thanh toán VNPay (nếu có route riêng)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/vnpay/create-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "674c1234567890abcdef9999",
  "amount": 530000,
  "order_description": "Thanh toán đơn hàng #674c12",
  "bank_code": ""
}

###

### 4. Tạo link thanh toán MoMo (nếu có)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/momo/create-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "674c1234567890abcdef9999",
  "amount": 530000,
  "order_info": "Thanh toán đơn hàng #674c12"
}
